SELECT c."Code", c."Name", c0."CollegeCode", c0."LicenseCode", c0."CollegeLicenseGroupingCode", c1."CollegeCode", c1."PracticeCode"
FROM "CollegeLookup" AS c
LEFT JOIN "CollegeLicense" AS c0 ON c."Code" = c0."CollegeCode"
LEFT JOIN "CollegePractice" AS c1 ON c."Code" = c1."CollegeCode"
ORDER BY c."Code", c0."CollegeCode", c0."LicenseCode", c1."CollegeCode", c1."PracticeCode"
